meta_description: Brawl Stars Championship is on! Interact with the show for a chance to earn in-game rewards!
gen_old_browser_desc: Your browser is too outdated to use this website, sorry
gen_error_desc: This could be due to a technical issues on your side (such as your internet connection) or our side (servers being down). Please try again later.
gen_reconnecting_description: Oof! A network error occurred. We are trying to reconnect - please be patient.
gen_error_multiple_sockets_desc: Another device is connected using the same Supercell ID. You can only continue watching with one device. You can take back control below.
no_broadcast_title: The stream will be back shortly
no_broadcast_desc: There is currently no stream available, please check back again soon.
logout_modal_desc_gametag: To change Supercell ID accounts, you must log out of this one first.
logout_modal_desc_standard: Are you sure you want to log out?
login_desc: To begin interacting, log in with your Supercell ID. Just enter your Supercell ID email to get a verification code.
login_modal_desc: To log in, enter your Supercell ID email and we'll email you a verification code.
login_error: Oh no! Your email address is invalid. Please try again.
login_error_pin: Oops! The verification code is invalid. Please try again.
login_register: You can register a new account in any Supercell ID game.
scid_modal_desc: When you connect your games to a Supercell ID account, you can save and transfer games across devices and operating systems.
scid_modal_how: How do I get a Supercell ID?
scid_modal_instruction_1: 1. Open a Supercell game on your mobile device
scid_modal_instruction_5: 5. Follow the instructions displayed on the screen
pin_sent: A verification code has been sent to {email}. Please enter the code to continue.
pin_recent: Please make sure to use the most recent code sent to your email.
pin_resend: Didn't receive a code? Be sure to check your email spam folder. Otherwise ****Click here**** to get a new code.
login_explainer_desc: Do you want to vote on the MVP or the outcome of matches, all while earning sweet rewards?
login_reward_desc: You are signed in. You can now predict games and earn rewards - best of luck and enjoy the show!
login_fail_no_game_desc: You don't have a Brawl Stars account associated to your Supercell ID account. Please download the game and sign in with your Supercell ID to get started.
predict_closed: Opens after Day {day_nr} live stream ends
pre_cd_desc: Watch and interact with the Brawl Stars World Finals here!
pre_predict_title: Who do you think will win?
mid_rewatch_unavailable_description: The stream is processing and will be available shortly.
post_winner_title: Congratulations to 2021 Brawl Stars World Champions: {team_name}
post_next_season_title: Brawl Stars Championship will be back in 2022!
predict_submitted_desc: Your predictions for Day {day_nr} have been submitted! Check back when the stream starts to see the results!
predict_submitted_desc_alt: Your predictions have been submitted! Check back when the stream starts to see the results!
predict_closed_desc: Please check back in a bit, we are updating all the winners for day {day_nr}.
predict_closed_desc_alt: Please check back in a bit, we are updating all the winners for the event.
predict_started_desc: You can no longer input pre-event predictions. Check out the stream to enter your predictions live before each match.
predict_leave_title: Are you sure you want to leave?
predict_leave_desc: You haven't finished your predictions just yet. If you leave now, all your predictions so far will be lost. Predictions can also be placed during the show before every match.
predict_submitted_locked_desc: You have submitted your predictions and they are therefore locked. Make sure to come back and watch the stream when it starts to see if your predictions are correct!
live_dialog_out_of_sync_desc: For some reason you are no longer watching the live version of the stream and are not able to earn points currently.
live_dialog_fullscreen_desc: To go fullscreen, rotate your phone and position the image. Just make sure rotation lock is turned off!
vod_card_no_interact: You can't interact with this card
lang_picker_desc: This will change the language of the interface and the stream. Some languages have multiple streams and there you can select one you prefer
lang_picker_stream_no_streams: There are no streams available right now. Check back later
lang2_picker_desc: There are multiple streams available for your language, which one do you prefer?
